Hackberryan
===========

Getting Started
---------------

To get started with Hackberryan:
	git clone git://github.com/shawe/Hackberryan

Once it's fully downloaded you can execute the script Hackberryan.sh with:
	./Hackberryan.sh
And complete the dialogs for have a personalized image for your Hackberry.

Or also you can edit the "config" file for specify your default values, and the script only ask to you the root password when it is needed.


